<h3>Language Files</h3>

<p>
  To change a blog localization, copy the language file below to the <code>.blaze/lang/</code> directory, and set the <code>blog.lang</code> option accordingly. Currently available localizations (with many thanks to Angel Abad, Martin Pavelek, Igor Ramos Tiburcio, Ton Kersten, Romain, and burner, who kindly provided translations to their language) are:
</p>

